# AEON Core - Assets Directory

This directory contains visual assets for the AEON Core project.

## Contents

### /diagrams
- Architecture diagrams
- Protocol flowcharts
- System topology visuals
- Consciousness transfer diagrams

### /screenshots (optional)
- Demo screenshots
- Simulation outputs
- UI mockups

## File Formats

Recommended formats:
- Diagrams: `.svg`, `.png` (vector preferred)
- Screenshots: `.png`
- Videos: `.mp4` (short demos only)

## Git Note

The `.gitkeep` file ensures this directory is tracked by Git even when empty.

Add actual assets as the project develops.

